title: Divisional Round Recap with NFL Super Friends (Football 1/14)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Sean Wagner-McGough, Ryan Wilson and John Breech to break down the Divisional Round weekend action, including a win by the Chiefs over the Colts (2:00), the Rams dominating performance over the Cowboys (12:00), the Patriots destruction of the Chargers (29:30) and the Saints squeaking by the Eagles (45:00) and make their early picks for AFC Championship Game and NFC Championship Game (55:00).
